40
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:14,356
Yeah, it's okay.

41
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:16,116
I can take care of myself.

42
00:02:16,140 --> 00:02:18,426
You know, I was on my way to breakfast.

43
00:02:18,450 --> 00:02:20,766
The restaurant's just
a few blocks from here,

44
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:22,806
have you had breakfast yet?

45
00:02:22,830 --> 00:02:27,830
Wait, you were the one who clapped.

46
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:31,833
Yeah, your presentation was inspired.

47
00:02:33,570 --> 00:02:37,956
You didn't think it was
boring or a pile of platitudes?

48
00:02:37,980 --> 00:02:40,593
No, you could tell
it was from the heart.

49
00:02:41,970 --> 00:02:43,623
Do you like poached eggs?

50
00:02:45,090 --> 00:02:48,126
So have you held any office,

51
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:51,063
and I mean any political office at all?

52
00:02:52,266 --> 00:02:53,076
President.

53
