103
00:05:28,442 --> 00:05:30,859
(calm music)

104
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:37,413
I think we're here.

105
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,563
Okay, gimme a second.

106
00:05:41,712 --> 00:05:43,026
All right, you're all set.

107
00:05:43,050 --> 00:05:44,283
I know how this works.

108
00:05:45,273 --> 00:05:46,563
Mind your head.

109
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:51,175
Ah, okay.

110
00:05:51,199 --> 00:05:52,749
Okay, approaching the stairs.

111
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:57,813
This is Oberoende.

112
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,536
Nice touch.

113
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,646
What?

114
00:06:02,670 --> 00:06:03,670
The doormat.

115
00:06:04,957 --> 00:06:06,276
Oh, thanks.

116
00:06:06,300 --> 00:06:07,673
And I see you're a CPA.

117
00:06:08,664 --> 00:06:10,116
I am.

118
00:06:10,140 --> 00:06:11,140
Ring the doorbell.

119
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:13,896
Don't you have a key?

120
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:16,203
Sure, but just do it.

121
00:06:17,670 --> 00:06:19,515
Okay.

122
00:06:19,539 --> 00:06:22,697
("Oberoende Anthem")

123
00:06:22,721 --> 00:06:23,721
What is that?

124
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,013
Oberoende national anthem.

125
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,611
Shall we?

126
00:06:29,635 --> 00:06:30,635
Okay.

127
00:06:31,388 --> 00:06:33,351
(door beeps)

128
00:06:33,375 --> 00:06:34,375
In we go.

129
00:06:42,930 --> 00:06:44,283
This is my office.

130
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:50,043
Those are my certificates,

131
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:55,053
and those are my collection of telephones.

132
00:07:04,051 --> 00:07:06,634
(upbeat music)

133
00:07:21,697 --> 00:07:22,836
Huh?

134
