You can't wear those in public.

135
00:07:24,990 --> 00:07:26,646
Why not?

136
00:07:26,670 --> 00:07:28,473
Definitely a stereotype.

137
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,794
Oh.

138
00:07:30,818 --> 00:07:32,073
If I'm blind, I'm blind.

139
00:07:32,940 --> 00:07:35,016
Maybe an operation could help.

140
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,966
