president, we can find the money.

142
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:44,193
Oh cool.

143
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:47,178
So what do you think?

144
00:07:47,202 --> 00:07:49,956
Oh, definitely not another country,

145
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:54,366
but then again, in your mind it could be.

146
00:07:54,390 --> 00:07:58,353
This is my office,
base of my operations.

147
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,900
And where do you live?

148
00:08:02,693 --> 00:08:05,110
(calm music)

149
00:08:06,930 --> 00:08:08,013
Welcome Oberoende.

150
00:08:12,653 --> 00:08:15,570
(enchanting music)

151
00:08:32,310 --> 00:08:33,396
(enchanting music)

152
00:08:33,420 --> 00:08:34,420
What do you think?

153
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:40,863
Yeah, this is more like it.

154
00:08:44,970 --> 00:08:45,970
Beautiful.

155
00:08:46,758 --> 00:08:48,306
We can have a feast in here

156
00:08:48,330 --> 00:08:50,766
