161
00:09:17,353 --> 00:09:19,770
(calm music)

162
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:27,066
Is this where you sleep?

163
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:28,090
Usually.

164
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:37,176
Looks comfortable.

165
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,333
Oh, it's very comfortable.

166
00:09:41,310 --> 00:09:43,323
Would you like to check it out?

167
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,000
Not now.

168
00:09:47,530 --> 00:09:49,947
(calm music)

169
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,456
Where do you keep your clothes?

170
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,863
Oh, in the closet.

171
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:13,950
Okay.

172
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,067
Mm-mm.

