175
00:10:24,270 --> 00:10:26,853
Um, is there something
wrong with my clothes?

176
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:32,496
One would only have to
look in a mirror to know.

177
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,520
Hmm.

178
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:36,483
Does this mean you're dressing me up?

179
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:40,173
Yeah, dressed up you won't look bad.

180
00:10:42,630 --> 00:10:45,396
Yup, we can definitely
make use of this space,

