185
00:11:06,937 --> 00:11:09,937
(people chattering)

186
00:11:19,950 --> 00:11:24,513
Hi, I'm Patrick Lee.

187
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:31,083
Thank you for coming here.

188
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:36,603
Thank you for filling out the cards.

189
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,770
And uh...

190
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:45,366
Thank you for your donations.

191
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:47,136
We want you to know

192
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:50,226
