202
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:23,466
It's a staple of the
(indistinct) circuit.

203
00:12:23,490 --> 00:12:26,913
It's born of a time
when that's all we had.

204
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:30,487
Yes, I know that.

205
00:12:33,090 --> 00:12:37,446
I wanna thank you for
putting all this together.

206
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:40,250
It's very impressive what you did, it's...

