00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,876
Excuse me for a moment.

208
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:44,643
A good friend of mine is here.

209
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:48,837
(calm music)

210
00:13:00,469 --> 00:13:03,126
I am Patrick Lee, nice to meet you.

211
00:13:03,150 --> 00:13:03,960
We met.

212
00:13:03,984 --> 00:13:05,826
Have you forgotten my name already?

213
00:13:05,850 --> 00:13:07,266
Samuel Brightcloud.

214
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:08,733
Oh right, Sam.

215
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:11,763
Celeste is really something.

216
00:13:14,070 --> 00:13:17,016
Do you know how she got
so many people to show up?

217
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,723
Don't you know who she is?

218
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:21,190
No.

219
00:13:22,410 --> 00:13:26,136
