and come here to California

222
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:33,966
and many of her followers came with her.

223
00:13:33,990 --> 00:13:35,616
Is she a politician?

224
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:40,640
No, a born leader, like
Mankiller before her.

225
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:42,366
Mankiller?

226
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:45,486
Wilma Mankiller, the first woman Chief

227
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:46,713
of the Cherokee nation.

228
00:13:47,972 --> 00:13:50,389
(calm music)

229
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:58,749
("Oberoende Anthem")

230
00:14:01,765 --> 00:14:02,848
I'm coming!

231
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,277
I'm almost there.

232
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,586
Patrick Lee?

233
00:14:14,610 --> 00:14:15,457
Yes.

234
00:14:15,481 --> 00:14:17,496
Oh, I have a package for you.

235
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,816
Is it my new eyes?

236
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,986
That's right.

237
00:14:20,010 --> 00:14:21,663
Oh, thank God for insurance.

238
