Vargas reporting for KSMX News.

240
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:40,176
Now while most of you know,
presidential candidates,

241
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:42,936
there are some that are not
as popular or as famous,

242
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:45,606
but still have that intent
to win the big prize

243
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,836
come this November.

244
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:48,786
So today we are gonna introduce you

245
00:14:48,810 --> 00:14:52,446
to a hopeful local candidate
by the name of Patrick Lee.

246
00:14:52,470 --> 00:14:54,126
As we interview him here,

247
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:56,826
inside his national campaign headquarters

248
00:14:56,850 --> 00:14:59,406
located in Los Angeles.

249
00:14:59,430 --> 00:15:00,696
Good afternoon.

250
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,856
Mr. Lee, I hear you're
running for president

251
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:04,023
of the United States?

252
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,876
Yes, what do you want?

253
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,856
