265
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:37,713
You don't need to wear
these for this interview.

266
00:15:40,107 --> 00:15:41,107
Ah, of course.

267
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:45,006
Mr. Lee, we're actually
wanting to feature you

268
00:15:45,030 --> 00:15:47,436
and do this interview to
put it in our segment,

269
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:49,296
it's called "Daylight."

270
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:51,546
